yearly_subsetter <- function(year) {sf_weather %>%
  select( c(DATE, TMAX, TMIN) ) %>%
  separate(DATE, c('YEAR', 'MONTH', 'DAY'), sep = '-', remove = FALSE) %>%
  filter(YEAR == year) %>%
  mutate('TAVG' = (TMAX+TMIN)/2 ) %>%
  group_by(MONTH) %>%
  summarise('MAX_MONTH_TEMP' = max(TAVG))
}
